<rss version="2.0" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" xmlns:ss="http://contenthub.aol.com/slideshow/"><channel><title><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></title><link/> https://www.engadget.com/ <description><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></description><language> en-US</language><copyright>版权所有雅虎 2023</copyright><pubDate> Tue, 05 Sep 2023 19:43:32 +0000</pubDate><generator>雅虎 http://yahoo.com </generator><item><title><![CDATA[TikTok job postings point to social features to help it compete with Meta]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> TikTok 似乎已准备好让该平台更接近成熟的社交网络。正如<em>Axios</em> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.axios.com/2023/09/05/tiktok-social-networking-messaging-features">发现的那样</a>，该公司发布了新的职位列表，重点关注社交网络功能和扩展的直接消息传递。一篇“产品经理 - TikTok 社交”帖子 <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://careers.tiktok.com/position/7097101084908603661/detail">写道</a>，该公司希望在“用户之间建立有意义的社交联系”。</p><p>据报道，这些职位列表与组织内部对保留和提高用户参与度的担忧有关。 <em>Axios</em>援引公司内部消息人士的话说：“在 TikTok 内部，人们担心，当用户想与朋友讨论 TikTok 视频时，他们会在其他社交媒体和消息应用程序上分享 TikTok 视频。”移动工程师的招聘信息称，候选人将专注于“建立一个可靠且适应性强的平台，使用户能够在 TikTok 上与现实生活中的朋友无缝会面和互动，并鼓励他们彼此分享生活时刻并保持联系”他们在哪里。”</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>扩展 TikTok 的消息传递功能似乎是最重要的。据<em>Axios</em>称，一份后端技术负责人的职位清单承认，该公司的消息传递能力还处于“起步阶段”。该帖子称，受聘人员将“探索和实施多元化的社交解决方案”，同时提到创建“独特的 TikTok 社交解决方案”消息。</p><p> TikTok 的根基是<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-11-27-tiktok-bytedance-makeup-uighur.html">病毒式视频</a>，其社交功能大多仅限于点赞、评论和转发等外围互动。随着 Instagram 等竞争对手平台整合了更多<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tiktok-photo-mode-instagram-194215693.html">类似 TikTok 的功能</a>，该公司通过扩大社交功能来回报大家的青睐似乎是合乎逻辑的。然而，它强调，在尝试新事物时，视频仍然是其身份的核心。 TikTok 发言人告诉<em>Axios</em> ：“娱乐频道一直是 TikTok 商业模式的核心，即使我们正在尝试新功能来增强用户体验。”</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/tiktok-job-postings-point-to-social-features-to-help-it-compete-with-meta-194332559.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/tiktok-job-postings-point-to-social-features-to-help-it-compete-with-meta-194332559.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 4c03a956-17ba-4a77-85ce-7b387c177040</guid><dc:creator>威尔·尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 05 Sep 2023 19:43:32 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693943014</ingested><modified> 2023-09-05T19:43:38+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="5760" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/4a3bedd0-4c20-11ee-be69-143fa016e6c6" width="8640"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="5760" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/4a3bedd0-4c20-11ee-be69-143fa016e6c6" width="8640"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ASSOCIATED PRESS]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[FILE - The icon for the video sharing TikTok app is seen on a smartphone, Feb. 28, 2023, in Marple Township, Pa. The state of Montana is asking a federal judge to allow its ban on downloading TikTok to take effect in January, even though the company argues i